Project Features:
    • Projects:
        ◦ create and manage your projects in Curq by asigning project managers, employees, members and conecting your projects with costemers.
    • Tasks
        ◦ asign employees and members to diferent tasks conect them to Sales orders
    • Kanban
        ◦ orgenise your projects and tasks in diferent stages and defign your proses with the kanban view
    • set deadling
        ◦ set deadlines and allocate the amount of hours that can be spend on your projects and tasks
    • Reporting:
        ◦ Generate reports on customer ratings and tasks analysis.
